<descript>
<abstract>
New York Commuter Rail Stations, 2026 is a line theme representing the Long Island Rail Road and Metro-North Railroad stations as of 2026. This dataset was derived from the New York State data repository (at https://data.ny.gov/Transportation/MTA-Rail-Stations/wxmd-5cpm/about_data) in March 2026. Attribute information includes information about the line served, station name, track title, station and parking map URL and accessibility status. Columbia Libraries staff has provided the data in the geopackage format in state plane coordinates, and a codebook and a has been included in the download package.
</abstract>
</descript>
